---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-primary text-white mt-20">
  <div class="container-wide py-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-4">도시산책</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          도시의 풍경과 일상을 담는 미디어 블로그.<br />
          걷다 보면 보이는 것들을 기록합니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">바로가기</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a href="/posts" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">전체 글</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/about" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">소개</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">RSS 피드</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

